snippet.title: Cats With Guns - Xbox Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Make strategic decisions on the middle of the battle and go from a small kitten to a powerful and intimidating feline. Evolve your cat and overwhelm the enemy forces with powerful abilities. Fight sheer enemy numbers with a huge firepower and defeat the generals until you reach Meowstopia. Get it now on Xbox! #idatxbox #idxbox
https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/cats-with-guns-xbox/9p878n714ffj
